/ralph-loop:ralph-loop "You are implementing a development task in this repository.

Goal:
Read goals from the GOAL.md file

Process:
- Maintain PLAN.md with the next 1–3 steps.
- After each step append results to PROGRESS.md.
- Keep changes small and reversible.
- Run tests before and after modifications:
  cd /workspaces/alpine/retirement-calculator && npm test

Stop when the goal is completed and tests pass.

When finished print exactly: DONE_DONE_DONE"
